<br>
&quot;Are ye not up for the task at hand young one?&quot;<br>
<br>
*Moves his eyes to Kitria*<br>
<br>
&quot;I have not broken any agreement, I have in fact gone beyond<br>
what was needed to better your son, he is a warrior yet still a child, ye nor your family of witches cannot teach him those ways, aye ye may be powerful, but to much time with ye noses in a book has done nothing to keep your combat abilities sharp, to me I see him as a brand new blade, hot off the anvil, dulled yet ready to be sharpend, ye can not offer him that, the Lust is nothing but soldiers and trainers.&quot;<br>
<br>
*Standing back to address the whole room, Rebelle watches as his wife leaves, a quiet sigh escapes him before continuing*<br>
<br>
&quot;Seraphimm has been givin the chore of strengthening Ferdar's ability to withstand pain, she will show him hurt of the flesh until he is able to shrug it off like rain off his armor.<br>
Then he shall begin the hurt of the mind, I will show him how to strengthen his mind beyond the limits of endurance, beyond<br>
the horizen of insanity and back.&quot; <br>
Until the time this task givin to young Ferdar is complete<br>
he will have but one hour a day to write his family and send them his best wishes, the other 23 hours will be spent in deep<br>
study of pain, no sleep, little food and water, when ye see him again he will no longer be the child ye see now, he will be a man, then he will begin his first assignment for the Lust.<br>
After completion he will join the Ranks of the Lust and be free to have, the pleasures of the flesh with his wife to be and to <br>
return to spend time with his mother and family.<br>
There is no discussion in this matter this is our way.<br>
either he fails or he succeeds, it is up to him.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a> <b>5</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=201&stop=220>11</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=221&stop=240>12</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showMessageRange?topicID=448.topic&start=241&stop=241>13</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showPrevMessage?topicID=448.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showNextMessage?topicID=448.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm47.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=100><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/